@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aocarc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.88
    tmp = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.50 / v2 + 0.11)) / v0)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.14)) * tmp)
    v1 = (wp.sin(v1) / wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.71)))
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.26 - v2 + 0.94) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.70)) * wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.18)))
    v0 = wp.exp(v2)
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
